{"tid":1629011,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"想問下泛民議員重有冇落現場陪你地抗爭？","createTime":"2019-10-06T05:54:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T04:07:59.000Z","uid":13084,"like":1,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"b319da0c5a2dcf478701b3fcfef72564e3891cb0","tid":1629011,"uid":13084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T05:54:04.000Z","msg":"發生左咁多事件之後，大家有冇留意泛民而家除左開記者會之外？重有冇落場抗爭？<br />\n鄺神呢？林卓庭呢？譚文豪呢？去哂邊？<br />\n佢哋由頭到尾有冇講過&rdquo;不割席，不分化，不篤灰&rdquo;？<br />\n我唔係想分化你地，而係唔希望你地比仇恨蒙蔽雙眼<br />\n睇清楚諗清楚，再咁落去邊個蝕底，最後又有邊個得益？<br />\n千萬唔好忘記泛民d閪行<br />\n永遠去到關鍵時刻，泛民就會出賣你地<br />\n<br />\n希望你地諗下之後條路應該點行好<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n五大訴求<br />\n缺一不可"},{"pid":"4e1e6e9e8a956272ff005c1f7ef646ee5ac0e2ef","tid":1629011,"uid":35924,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T05:55:56.000Z","msg":"又狙擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3e84beb234a7aa8be3e5515b63b51676fd7907a","tid":1629011,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T05:56:18.000Z","msg":"【行動】盡快整理所有警暴片段，同納粹暴行做對比，爭取西方實際行動支持香港<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1628720\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1628720</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n請幫手推文支持<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1628720\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1628720</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"626f3585c4f726633d11de2ad4cf189b763c89a0","tid":1629011,"uid":81569,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T05:56:25.000Z","msg":"收皮啦屌你老母樓主<br />\n為議員賣命都唔割"},{"pid":"6f538d5a4b0d63f3ca7627942034ca8bf6ca1469","tid":1629011,"uid":83582,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T05:57:33.000Z","msg":"搞緊JR, 雖然失敗左"},{"pid":"4a56f6fcc96e962545ef45b84e843b458640b5f1","tid":1629011,"uid":79278,"like":3,"dislike":0,"scor